{"tid":1108717,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[月供股票] 2019年4月(5) 問定唔問 睇完#1先好問","createTime":"2019-04-16T06:02:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T08:13:41.000Z","uid":42533,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"08bacb20717a728b11c639d9cf3d44e91ed833b3","tid":1108717,"uid":42533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T06:02:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中銀個人客戶服務熱線 +852 3988 2388<br />\n投資服務熱線 +852 3988 2688</span></span><br />\n  <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">追完post先問好嗎？<br />\n再問手續費就屌老母<br />\n再問股息點入Ticker就屌老母</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n榮譽會員:間諜巴打(教大家月供2800), 朱千雪讓我哭巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n月供po狗鐵主席: i-vtec <strong>（尚欠每人50加1股2388）</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y7moU2L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY7moU2L.jpg&h=f2f01690&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Photo credit: 消委會</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新手知識：</span></ins></strong><br />\n問：咩叫月供股票？<br />\n答：每月用你指定既金額，購買你指定既股票。<br />\n例：你set左月供$2000盈富、$2000騰訊、$2000匯豐，假設你用中銀黎做月供，會係每月既第十一日買入。假設盈富個日係$20一股，你會買到100股，騰訊係$201一股，你會買到9股，即$1809，銀行只會扣你$1809。<br />\n<br />\n問：月供股票有咩好？<br />\n答：<br />\n1）低入場費：如果你睇好騰訊，但佢一手要大約兩萬蚊，但你冇咁多錢，月供就幫到你。你可以每月$5000咁供。<br />\n2）平均成本：假設騰訊三個月既價係：$170、$180、$190，你同樣都係月供$5000，係第一個月你會買到29股，第二個月買到27股，第三個月買到26股，變相平個陣買多啲，貴個陣買小啲。個平均買入價會係$15000/(29+27+26)=$182.9。<br />\n3）減低心理因素：由於每月都係指定個日入貨，我地唔需要睇價入，平時好多時會見佢貴，冇入到，點知就升到咩咁。<br />\n<br />\n問：啲碎股點算好？有冇息收？<br />\n答：係有息收的，唔需要草夠一手先有。至於會唔會賣唔出？中銀就承諾可以以正價沽出碎股，所以唔洗擔心。<br />\n<br />\n問：用邊間？收費如何？<br />\n答：主要都係推介呢兩間：中銀，一通。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>中銀</ins>：可以用信用卡供，容易周轉，仲儲埋積分。<br />\n每個月$50，已包收息費、存倉、買入。除咗賣貨有其他收費，基本上可以話係全包價<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">包撚哂</span></span>，更可以以正價沽出碎股。<span style=\"color: red;\">(沽出照正常收費，詳情可以睇番收費表）</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://bochk.com/m/tc/investment/securities/monthly.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbochk.com%2Fm%2Ftc%2Finvestment%2Fsecurities%2Fmonthly.html&d=BdEUjZUsFG%2BHnlCy9NhCdwFhK%2BZ0PNwQmNlOVL%2F21oE%3D&h=d1eda0bd\" target=\"_blank\">http://bochk.com/m/tc/investment/securities/monthly.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>一通</ins>：所有交易都係$5，收息每次$5。如果你月供3隻，每月就係$15。（有錯請補充，因為我用中銀的）<br />\n<br />\n問：有咩記數app?<br />\n答：Ticker。非常清晰咁記錄你既交易同會自動幫你計你個平均買入價。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問：比較受歡迎既月供選擇？<br />\n答：盈富基金、騰訊、匯豐、建行、港鐵、煤氣、電能、港燈、領展。<br />\n<br />\n問：中銀幾號扣數，買入？<br />\n答：每月第十一日買入，第十日扣數，如果撞正非交易日，會順延。例如，十號係星期六，咁會下星期一先扣數，星期二買入，星期三出statement。<br />\n<br />\n問：mark數入唔入50好？<br />\n答：請自行決定。<br />\n<br />\n問：新手開始月供，想供$xxxxx 供咩好？/ 新手開始月供，供xxx定供xxx好？<br />\n答：你供比我？<br />\n<br />\n問：中銀ebanking邊到睇買入價？<br />\n答：電子結單-&gt;證券交易<br />\n<br />\n問：點解仲未扣數/入數？<br />\n答：出左statement都見唔到既話，請自行與中銀職員聯絡。<br />\n <br />\n問：點解揀唔到用信用卡供？<br />\n答：上ebanking &gt;個人設定 揀番張信用卡出黎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講住咁多先，其他留待其他巴絲補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n一通幾錢一個月？收息點計手續費？聽講個SYSTEM成日壞？會唔會買唔到貨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊間股票多選擇啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n渣打免佣好似抵啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n匯豐長期免手續費，唔係仲平咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢排見南商做緊優惠？有無巴打知詳情？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買夠10萬轉返去銀行得唔得？有存款保障？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後射去中銀收幾錢？中銀係咪免手續費？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係全免？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中銀信用卡供股可以儲積分？我上網搵唔到嘅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中銀信用卡嗰邊未見扣數？有無巴打扣咗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但今日開咗張信用卡，今個月都會轉到用信用卡扣數？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開戶要帶咩文件？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n月供用邊間最平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中銀用邊張信用卡供有優惠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用一通定中銀供抵啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家咁貴 月供係唔係好唔抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遲啲股市跌 月供係唔係好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隻股票唔會郁 月供係唔係賺唔到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中銀月供 點樣睇到買入平均價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有以上問題？有個懶人包可以答到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">伸手黨懶人包Link</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:<br />\n<a href=\"http://bfy.tw/FKYu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbfy.tw%2FFKYu&d=BdEUjZUsFG%2BHnlCy9NhCdwFhK%2BZ0PNwQmNlOVL%2F21oE%3D&h=8eae65ac\" target=\"_blank\">http://bfy.tw/FKYu</a><br />\n<br />\n再唔係就... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中銀個人客戶服務熱線 +852 3988 2388<br />\n投資服務熱線 +852 3988 2688</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>此post純屬討論，並不為任何投資決策負責。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n月供po港鐵主席ok-i笑話幾則:<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/182901_4b5c03449524e0ccb4a8f5421f03dc9a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F182901_4b5c03449524e0ccb4a8f5421f03dc9a.png&h=cf5a9acd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/19/101801_91b3406b0bf44beffc94299720f994d4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F19%2F101801_91b3406b0bf44beffc94299720f994d4.png&h=b3b75a8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1XehZqd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1XehZqd.png&h=0adafe2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kv4g2kR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKv4g2kR.jpg&h=8addec9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/igZ5hJ9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FigZ5hJ9.png&h=e557c0d1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"382df171391818188756888382bab69015955436","tid":1108717,"uid":42533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T06:59:35.000Z","msg":"[月供股票] 2019年4月(5) 問定唔問 睇完#1先好問<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1108912\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1108912</a>"},{"pid":"be9b58d0af359d6e984a5114b834f985cc9029a5","tid":1108717,"uid":170256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T08:12:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/ass